{"tid":2440830,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"根本推廣疫苗就等於人口滅絕計劃","createTime":"2021-03-10T08:31:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T04:45:50.000Z","uid":222614,"like":12,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"31b0bd393d488d0ab7ca80b6ee5be55c45d502db","tid":2440830,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:31:33.000Z","msg":"第一大謬誤：疫苗只要唔係中國製就安全<br />\n<br />\n事實：<br />\n每個人嘅體質及病歷都不同，身體對疫苗所作出嘅反應都不同<br />\n化學物質進入人體後所涉及嘅化學反應太多<br />\n若不幸致死，亦難以證明與疫苗有關<br />\n但疫苗可以作為致死嘅觸發點<br />\n<br />\n舉例：<br />\n接種輝瑞而死嘅人，接種科興未必有事<br />\n接種科興而死嘅人，接種輝瑞未必有事<br />\n<br />\n另外，輝瑞同Moderna 所生產嘅疫苗比科興更早出現死亡或嚴重副作用個案<br />\n<br />\n美國一名醫生注射疫苗後死亡<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2367728\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2367728</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n結論：<br />\n<br />\n推廣疫苗，刻意淡化致死風險係極不負責任同惡毒嘅行為<br />\n<br />\n將某幾隻疫苗同其他疫苗比較，然後話「打邊隻會危險啲，邊隻安全啲」亦係極之誤導，因為你唔知身體會對邊隻疫苗產生較多或較少嘅不良反應"},{"pid":"85a87f307a8a7133bb53f96b1c628aaee6efaa6e","tid":2440830,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:32:24.000Z","msg":"直播注射疫苗後暈到嘅女護士，至今仍然生死未卜<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2401681\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2401681</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"008384f0851c635b48e3fa238eed64512c685ae5","tid":2440830,"uid":222614,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:34:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1565704-20201217.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1565704-20201217.htm&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwpleBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=79c71e42\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1565704-20201217.htm&h=2089cd4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1565704-20201217.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1e91c012089a6c84c9b75b862db4aef2486b762a","tid":2440830,"uid":222614,"like":0,