=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你有病唔好食藥，甚至只飲營養液<br />\n任何藥物甚至食物都有一定危險，主要係過敏反應<br />\n問題係機率上好過咩都唔做就得，特別係仲要考慮經濟"},{"pid":"a928009508f9429cc5c002204827126351adb62e","tid":2440830,"uid":351022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:42:56.000Z","msg":"如果係相比起每日死亡嘅個案呢? 打針可唔可以打到每日死十幾廿個?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oM04mz7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoM04mz7.png&h=4acde4b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.jpost.com/health-science/coronavirus-71-percent-less-deaths-45-percent-less-critical-patients-since-january-peak-661296\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jpost.com%2Fhealth-science%2Fcoronavirus-71-percent-less-deaths-45-percent-less-critical-patients-since-january-peak-661296&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwpleBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=3a860126\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.jpost.com/health-science/coronavirus-71-percent-less-deaths-45-percent-less-critical-patients-since-january-peak-661296</a><br />\n<blockquote>Some 14 people died of COVID-19 on Sunday, according to a report by the Health Ministry on Monday. In the past week, the highest number of people passing away from the virus over 24 hours was 21, marking a significant decrease compared to what happened in previous weeks &mdash; on January 24, 79 patients died in a single day.</blockquote>"},{"pid":"63918497f456554c1b917060f39efe0a47ecf81c","tid":2440830,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:43:19.000Z","msg":"較早前嘅集體疫苗致死個案<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ctvnews.ca/health/coronavirus/norway-reviewing-deaths-of-frail-and-elderly-patients-vaccinated-against-covid-19-1.5272547\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ctvnews.ca%2Fhealth%2Fcoronavirus%2Fnorway-reviewing-deaths-of-frail-and-elderly-patients-vaccinated-against-covid-19-1.5272547&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwpleBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhW